## Why This Is Asked

This question evaluates practical knowledge of API testing for streaming systems, with emphasis on per-tenant isolation, backpressure management, reconnection semantics, and resilience against downstream failures. It tests understanding of both protocol-level concerns (HTTP/2, WebSocket) and operational concerns (fault injection, monitoring).

## Key Concepts

